<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Lottery Prediction</title>
    <style type="text/css">
      body {
        font-family: "Nunito Sans", sans-serif;
        font-size: 14px;
        background-color: #f4f4f4;
        color: #222222;
        text-align: center;
      }
      .email-wrapper {
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        background-color: #ffffff;
        padding: 20px;
        border-radius: 8px;
      }
      .email-header {
        background-color: #0070f3;
        padding: 16px 20px;
        color: #ffffff;
        border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0;
      }
      .code {
        font-size: 20px;
        font-weight: bold;
        background-color: #f3f3f3;
        padding: 10px;
        border-radius: 4px;
        display: inline-block;
      }
      .footer {
        margin-top: 20px;
        font-size: 12px;
        color: #555;
      }
      .title {
        font-size: 16px;
        text-align: center;
        justify-content: center;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="email-wrapper">
      <div class="email-header">
        <h1 class="title">Lottery Prediction Results</h1>
      </div>
      <p>Dear Michael,</p>
      <p>Here are the latest lottery predictions:</p>
      <p><strong>Draw:</strong> <%= draw %></p>
      <p><strong>Date:</strong> <%= date %></p>
      <p><strong>Predicted Numbers:</strong></p>
      <div class="code"><%= predictedNumbers.join(', ') %></div>
      <p><strong>Prediction Accuracy:</strong> <%= accuracy.toFixed(2) %>%</p>
      <div class="footer">
        <p>If you have any questions, contact us at michaelkpanti@gmail.com</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
